summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4916 for the improvement of West Holden Street from 35th avenue Southwest to California Avenue; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by constructing watermains and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 56325 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll , establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
